The Datadog Agent Integrations (also known as checks) supported by the
Datadog Agent on FreeBSD. This collection includes support for core
system metrics (disk, network, process) and popular applications like
Apache, MySQL, Nginx, PostgreSQL, Redis, and more.

This port also includes FreeBSD-specific integrations for monitoring
ZFS datasets and SMART disk health.

WWW: https://www.datadoghq.com/
